quote><blockquote><blockquote>套戲個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLuke會死？</blockquote><br />\n睇個名九成係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三主角一個現實死左<br />\n一個係戲比個仔隊死左<br />\nLuke睇怕都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得係佢自己都想終結JEDI姐</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n佢個句真係好灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明當年Luke好威水<br />\n白卜庭拉佢入dark side <br />\n佢拋低光劍拒殺老豆 幾堅決 幾有型<br />\n<br />\n佢已經(?)冇生仔 Skywalker已經絕後啦<br />\n佢仲要唔再教Jedi嘅話⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n不過話說cannon真係同legend差好遠咁</blockquote><br />\nluke 唔係想要平衡咩<br />\n平衡左應該唔會再分jedi同sith? last jedi既意思應該係咁？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前上網都睇過啲人討論有關咩先叫&quot;原力平衡&quot;<br />\n睇返1-3\b集 其實個時Jedi人數大大\b&gt;Sith<br />\n但佢地都要走去搵Skywalker呢個被選中嘅細佬<br />\n因為佢可以帶來原力平衡<br />\n如果數\b量平衡=原力平衡 <br />\n咁最簡單應該唔再收Padawan?<br />\n結果衰仔唔生性 入咗dark side 做埋sith lord 殺晒啲jedi⋯⋯<br />\n結果 咪終於好平衡囉 2個sith 2個jedi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好啦 其實有冇人對呢個\b平衡嘅概念有理解？"},{"pid":"91323f42c10fa1aa177a026dc4c7b619810c643e","tid":201312,"uid":55192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T02:15:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>套戲個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLuke會死？</blockquote><br />\n睇個名九成係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三主角一個現實死左<br />\n一個係戲比個仔隊死左<br />\nLuke睇怕都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得係佢自己都想終結JEDI姐</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n佢個句真係好灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明當年Luke好威水<br />\n白卜庭拉佢入dark side <br />\n佢拋低光劍拒殺老豆 幾堅決 幾有型<br />\n<br />\n佢已經(?)冇生仔 Skywalker已經絕後啦<br />\n佢仲要唔再教Jedi嘅話⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n不過話說cannon真係同legend差好遠咁</blockquote><br />\nluke 唔係想要平衡咩<br />\n平衡左應該唔會再分jedi同sith? last jedi既意思應該係咁？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nbig d要寫過個故事呀嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只係講下啫<br />\n<br />\n以前一路畫starwars漫畫、小說<br />\n啲人都係跟返個個概念 就係jedi 同 sith<br />\n但砍掉重練之後 就有一個叫knight of ren<br />\n已經好唔同<br />\n跟住又出現啲冇訓練都已經好強大嘅原力使用者<br />\n整體上好似已經唔同咗好多\b嘢 <br />\n<br />\n\b當然我希望唔好又係炸死星 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ccf9470315425b6fa97171894787933e89cd3a2","tid":201312,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T02:20:10.000Z","msg":"最後無事"},{"pid":"6ccc46617eb46d6d8b1cbc333eea24c82bf9a8bc","tid":201312,"uid":1670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T02:24:14.000Z","msg":"Anakin算唔算一直都係中緊平衡原力呢個預言<br />\n由前傳殺曬jedi學徒，兩邊各有anakin+白卜庭同yoda+obiwan <br />\n到正傳本來淨返luke一個jedi,但anakin都殺埋白卜庭。<br />\n雖然個時佢自己都死埋，但佢算唔算一直中緊被選中去平衡原力既人？"},{"pid":"64c3d8e365407288dec1a68e9d8f8459b14fe3a9","tid":201312,"uid":861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T02:29:14.000Z","msg":"又星戰 悶唔悶d呀<br />\n集集一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0841aebace2365674230f2248e1b277f8f3dda56","tid":201312,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T02:36:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>套戲個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLuke會死？</blockquote><br />\n睇個名九成係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三主角一個現實死左<br />\n一個係戲比個仔隊死左<br />\nLuke睇怕都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得係佢自己都想終結JEDI姐</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n佢個句真係好灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明當年Luke好威水<br />\n白卜庭拉佢入dark side <br />\n佢拋低光劍拒殺老豆 幾堅決 幾有型<br />\n<br />\n佢已經(?)冇生仔 Skywalker已經絕後啦<br />\n佢仲要唔再教Jedi嘅話⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n不過話說cannon真係同legend差好遠咁</blockquote><br />\nluke 唔係想要平衡咩<br />\n平衡左應該唔會再分jedi同sith? last jedi既意思應該係咁？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前上網都睇過啲人討論有關咩先叫&quot;原力平衡&quot;<br />\n睇返1-3\b集 其實個時Jedi人數大大\b&gt;Sith<br />\n但佢地都要走去搵Skywalker呢個被選中嘅細佬<br />\n因為佢可以帶來原力平衡<br />\n如果數\b量平衡=原力平衡 <br />\n咁最簡單應該唔再收Padawan?<br />\n結果衰仔唔生性 入咗dark side 做埋sith lord 殺晒啲jedi⋯⋯<br />\n結果 咪終於好平衡囉 2個sith 2個jedi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好啦 其實有冇人對呢個\b平衡嘅概念有理解？</blockquote><br />\nskywk個陣<br />\n啲game好似話vadar只係一個好普通既sith<br />\n係銀河其他地方有啲sith仲撚勁過白卜庭<br />\n<br />\n唔熟呢啲side story<br />\n有冇巴打講多啲<br />\n<br />\n同埋jedi好似去到邊都唔夠sith打咁"}]}